HEADWORD: Incommode
<hw>In`com*mode"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An inconvenience.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Strype.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incommodement</ent>⟦br⟧
